.claude/
_bmad/

# BMAD UX working scratch — screenshots, Playwright CLI logs, mockup
# iterations, and memlogs. Regenerable exploration output, not deliverables;
# the DESIGN.md/EXPERIENCE.md/mockups and reports under _bmad-output are tracked.
**/.working/
**/.playwright-cli/
**/.memlog.md
.bmad-loop/runs/
.bmad-loop/cache/
.bmad-loop/policy.toml
